items.statusDetails: Exception: Cannot use "remote" browser driver on localhost! Did you mean to connect to a remote Grid server such as BrowserStack or Sauce Labs? In that case, you must specify the "server" and "port" parameters on the command line! Example: --server=user:key@hub.browserstack.com --port=80
